            text: 'I also cleaned up the gameplay HUD because the original sections were slightly different heights, and once I noticed that, it started annoying me like a loose cupboard door. The HUD now behaves more like proper modules: score, notice, items, and lives. It is not final, but it is much cleaner.',
          },
