      },
      {
        type: 'note',
        title: 'UI Toolkit lesson learned',
        text: 'For this project, the Panel Settings asset needs to scale with screen size using a 1920x1080 reference. Constant Physical Size made the UI behave unpredictably between the 4K desktop and the MacBook.',
      },
      {
        type: 'paragraph',
