      {
        type: 'paragraph',
        content: [
          {
            text: 'During another quiet stretch, I created a few more prefabs, added double jump, and tried to reduce the problem where the player sometimes catches on platform edges. The double jump already feels useful for testing. The sticking issue is better after adding a zero-friction physics material, but it has not completely vanished. It is not bad enough to derail the morning, so it stays on the review list.',
          },
