    },
    {
      type: "paragraph",
      content: [
        {
          text: "The focus now is to start picking one or two items at a time and getting them properly working, while also starting to shape the actual levels. The scary unknowns are shrinking. The work is becoming more about finishing, tuning, and making the game feel good.",
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      type: "paragraph",
      content: [
        {
          text: "For the morning of 3rd June, the plan was to tackle the main menu ",
        },
        {
          text: "About",
          strong: true,
        },
        {
          text: " and ",
        },
        {
          text: "Quit",
          strong: true,
        },
        {
          text: " buttons, add an in-game pause menu, and take another look at the player sticking on platforms.",
