      type: "pullquote",
      text: "The scary unknowns are shrinking. The work is becoming more about finishing, tuning, and making the game feel good.",
    },
    {
      type: "paragraph",
      content: [
        {
          text: "While tracking down the player getting caught on platforms bug, I realized I had never actually made a proper ",
        },
        {
          text: "playerSpawner",
          code: true,
        },
        {
          text: " object. I had mostly just thrown the player into the scene and carried on. I thought creating the spawner/respawn structure would be a quick ten-minute task, but a little bad planning on my part, plus ",
        },
        {
          text: "Egotist",
          em: true,
